data.description: Beautiful 4-bedroom, 3-bath home in The Hampton Hills neighborhood close to Fairway Greens Park, the Northwest Greenway, and Pomerleau Lake! The front porch welcomes you into the open concept main level, which features beautiful hardwood floors, a spacious family room with gas fireplace, formal and informal dining, a large office, and a gourmet kitchen with center island, cherry cabinets, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances. There are four spacious bedrooms with large closets on the upper level, including the owner’s suite with a private full bath and walk-in closet. The walkout lower level is ready to be finished and includes carpet, sheetrock, and rough-ins for the bathroom and wet bar. Enjoy outdoor entertaining on the maintenance-free deck! Other features of this quality home include a convenient second floor laundry room, an attached 3-car garage, and beautiful landscaping with two raised garden beds. Ready to move in and make it your own!
